nd total bilirubin measured promptly, and cannabidiol treatment interrupted or discontinued as appropriate.', 'Synergism', '(Hepatotoxicity): Caution is advised if cannabidiol is used in patients who are currently receiving or have recently received treatment with other hepatotoxic agents, and vice versa.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/54889/', '', 'Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Anakinra, More', 'Tiagabine, Brivaracetam, Methsuximide, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Paramethadione, Perampanel, Fenfluramine, Eslicarbazepine, Phensuximide, Phenacemide, More', 1767369485);
